    "end": 4377197.0,
    "text": "And the last thing is that if you guys found any value in this dialogue. We feel that we should have more of these dialogues and more frequently. And, you know, enhanced communication is the key to, in my mind, the key to agile delivery. And climate action requires urgency, a sense of urgency. So that's kind of the driver for for us, suggesting that we meet more often and be able to react quickly to all the issues associated with climate action."
