    "text": "[FOREIGN LANGUAGE] And from the staff perspective, initiative. As you saw from our focus areas, 2 of our 6 focus areas, one was collaboration, one was education and outreach. So this is very important for us and for all of our planning efforts, like with our solid waste management plan. We wanted to make sure the public was engaged early and often, and we had a very successful survey with our solid waste management plan. Over 6,000 respondents— 600— what did I say? 6,000, sorry. I guess I'm over— is 600, sorry. Thank you for the correction. That would have been amazing, 6,000. So we've really received a lot of feedback from our community, and it's extremely important that we get input from the community. So for each project, we want to ensure that there's a very thorough education outreach perspective on our projects."
