    "start": 7481316.0,
    "end": 7522945.0,
    "text": "everything that he mentioned and all the initiatives and programs I agree with. I have been an advocate for the composting. I think especially with schools becoming involved with that, education is key. I'm, I'm really proud to see all the work that you guys have done with education, prevention, trying to educate and expand to our community, the preservation initiatives that you guys are doing as well. I do see that, and I know that our children do too. So thank you. I think that's all of the questions that I had and the information that I at this time am needing to be able to kind of steer you in the right direction as far as our priorities. Okay, thank you."
