    "speaker_source": "unresolved",
    "speaker_source_detail": "AssemblyAI could not identify speaker",
    "start": 7524149.0,
    "end": 7561256.0,
    "text": "May I just comment on, uh, Councilmember Bates's point? And it's well taken. Of course, from our perspective, we are the only committee that's important, and I realize that that if you have to give everybody else the same amount of time you give us, that would add up. I anticipate that what we're talking about is not so much an hour-and-a-half meeting every quarter, but to stay in touch more closely. And we— there are other avenues to do that. And if you would allow me to, we'll discuss this at our next meeting and get back to you with a couple of suggestions."
