    "start": 12202838.0,
    "end": 12227020.0,
    "text": "It was amazing. Thank you. We got so many great ideas, especially the fact that it's not just about imposing fees or fines or scaring folks. What are the solutions? Education. You know, what are the community projects that we can do to bring folks in together, whether it's a Buy Nothing Facebook, right? Like you guys talked about Goodwill and other ways to bring the community together. This was the best feedback. So thank you."
