    "speaker_source": "unresolved",
    "speaker_source_detail": "AssemblyAI could not identify speaker",
    "start": 14591563.0,
    "end": 14604514.0,
    "text": "I think so, but I want the council to— to— I think so, but I think I want the council to agree that that's the case. We are introducing a new element, so I want you all to be comfortable with that."
